An Act to Change the Name of Eighteenth Avenue Elementary School Located at Barangay San Roque, Quezon City, to Do単a Josefa Edralin Marcos Elementary School
Section 1. Eighteenth Avenue Elementary School located at Barangay San Roque, Quezon City, is hereby renamed Do単a Josefa Edralin Marcos Elementary School in honor of Do単a Josefa Edralin Marcos.
